data.description: Beautiful tranquil home on almost 5 acres. This 3 bedroom and 1 and 1/2 bath sits on a lot that has complete privacy and a beautiful mountain view! The main level of the home has an open floor plan. Upstairs you will find the 2 bedrooms and the master suite, which also features a loft. Outside you will find a very large heated garage and a fenced in barn that is perfect to keep horses or other livestock. The property also features a shared runway. Schedule now for a showing!
